nted%20interim%20bail%20to%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20leader%20in%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20case%20against%20him%2C%20but%20he%20remains%20in%20jail%20in%20the%20CBI%20case.%20This%20means%20that%20if%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20gives%20him%20the%20relief%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20will%20walk%20out%20of%20prison%20after%20over%20five%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20arrested%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20on%20June%2026.%20The%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20on%20August%205%20upheld%20his%20arrest%20as%20legal%20and%20said%20the%20CBI%20was%20able%20to%20establish%20that%20the%20AAP%20leader%20could%20influence%20witnesses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppearing%20for%20Mr%20Kejriwal%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%20Abhishek%20Singhvi%20said%20this%20is%20an%20unprecedented%20matter.%20The%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20he%20said%2C%20has%20got%20relief%20twice%20under%20the%20stringent%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act.%20The%20CBI%2C%20he%20said%2C%20had%20done%20as%20%26quot%3Binsurance%20arrest%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%2C%20he%20said%2C%20had%20arrested%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20after%20two%20years.%20%26quot%3BThree%20court%20orders%20are%20in%20my%20favour.%20This%20is%20an%20insurance%20arrest%2C%20so%20that%20he%20can%20be%20kept%20in%20jail%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singhvi%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singhvi%20said%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20needs%20to%20address%20three%20questions%20--%20is%20there%20a%20flight%20risk%3F%20will%20he%20tamper%20with%20evidence%3F%20will%20he%20influence%20witnesses%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20basis%20for%20CBI's%20arrest%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20was%20not%20cooperating.%20This%20issue%2C%20Mr%20Singhvi%20said%2C%20had%20been%20addressed%20in%20the%20past%20judgments%20that%20say%20an%20accused%20cannot%20be%20expected%20to%20incriminate%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArvind%20Kejriwal%20is%20a%20constitutional%20functionary%20and%20cannot%20be%20a%20flight%20risk.%20There%20can't%20be%20tampering%2C%20there%20are%20lakhs%20of%20documents%2C%20five%20chargesheets%20have%20been%20filed.%20There%20is%20also%20no%20risk%20of%20influencing%20witnesses.%20The%20triple%20test%20for%20bail%20is%20in%20my%20favour%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20person%20was%20found%20fit%20for%20release%20twice%2C%20once%20by%20Supreme%20Court%20too%20even%20under%20higher%20threshold%20of%20Section%2045%20(of%20PMLA).%20I%20am%20the%20most%20captive%20interrogatee%20you%20can%20find%2C%20ever.%20Just%20for%20insurance%20you%20arrested!%20No%20substantial%20material%20was%20demonstrated%20before%20special%20judge%20to%20justify%20my%20arrest%2C%20grounds%20were%20vague%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singhvi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20Justice%20Kant%20said%20while%20the%20bench%20will%20hear%20both%20sides%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20are%20wondering%20how%20long%20we%20should%20hear%20in%20a%20bail%20matter%2C%20do%20ordinary%20mortals%20get%20this%20much%20time%3F%26quot%3B%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20SV%20Raju%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20CBI%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20as%20much%20time%20as%20him%20(Singhvi)%2C%20at%20least.%26quot%3B%C2%A0Mr%20Singhvi%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20glad%20my%20lordships%20pointed%20that%20out.%20I%20will%20take%20till%2012%20so%20we%20can%20finish%20by%20lunch.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20the%20CBI's%20counsel%20asked%20if%20Mr%20Singhvi%20is%20arguing%20on%20bail%20or%20arrest%20and%20that%20he%20cannot%20mix%20the%20two.%C2%A0%26quot%3BTriple%20test%20satisfied%20fully.%20Every%20other%20possible%20co-accused%20has%20been%20released.%20I%20am%20taking%20about%20same%2C%20Vijay%20Nair%2C%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20Sanjay%20Singh%20and%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singhvi%20said%20multiple%20chargesheets%20have%20been%20filed.%20%26quot%3BProlonged%20incarceration%20cannot%20be%20there%2C%20is%20the%20triple%20test%20satisfied%3F%20yes%20it%20is...%20all%20the%20judgments%20held%20on%20these%20points...%20in%20the%20Manish%20Sisodia%20judgment%2C%20the%20court%20held%20that%20in%20this%20particular%20case%20of%20excise%20policy%2C%20trial%20is%20impossible%20to%20finish.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725519060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fl90rukv_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_21_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-arvind-kejriwal-walk-free-key-hearing-in-supreme-court-today-6494494%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20hearing%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20petitions%20seeking%20bail%20and%20challenging%20his%20arrest%20in%20the%20CBI%20case%20linked%20to%20the%20capital's%20now-scrapped%20liquor%20policy%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20India%20discovered%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725518720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113085574%2Cimgsize-92634.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fhow-india-discovered-jasprit-bumrah%2Farticleshow%2F113085362.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jasprit%20Bumrah's%20journey%20from%20playing%20gully%20cricket%20in%20Ahmedabad%20to%20becoming%20a%20standout%20bowler%20is%20notable.%20After%20nearly%20quitting%20cricket%20in%202012%2C%20he%20made%20a%20significant%20impact%20during%20the%202013%20Syed%20Mushtaq%20Ali%20T20%20tournament.%20His%20performance%20caught%20John%20Wright's%20attention%2C%20leading%20to%20his%20IPL%20debut%20with%20Mumbai%20Indians%20and%20eventual%20selection%20for%20India's%20national%20team.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Murder%20Case%20Against%20Actor%20Darshan%2C%20Photos%20Of%20Assault%20On%20Victim%20Surface%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20new%20twist%20in%20the%20kidnap%20and%20murder%20case%20against%20Kannada%20actor%20Darshan%2C%20photos%20allegedly%20showing%20the%20victim%20Renukaswamy%20being%20tortured%20before%20his%20death%20have%20surfaced%20on%20Thursday.%20The%20photos%20emerged%20after%20the%20Karnataka%20Police%20submitted%20a%203%2C991-page%20chargesheet%20in%20the%20murder%20case%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20news%20agency%20IANS%2C%20one%20of%20the%20photos%20shows%20Renukaswamy%2C%20shirtless%20and%20sitting%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20front%20of%20parked%20trucks%2C%20in%20tears.%20Another%20image%20shows%20him%20unconscious%20in%20front%20of%20a%20truck%20wearing%20a%20vest%20and%20blue%20jeans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIANS%20sources%20said%20the%20photos%20were%20found%20on%20the%20phone%20of%20Darshan's%20aide%20Pavan%20and%20were%20collected%20as%20evidence%20by%20the%20police%20department.%20The%20Karnataka%20police%20have%20not%20issued%20any%20official%20statement%20regarding%20the%20leaked%20photos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20say%20that%20Pavan%2C%20who%20is%20also%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20case%2C%20took%20the%20photos%20of%20Renukaswamy%20after%20kidnapping%2C%20assaulting%20and%20keeping%20him%20at%20a%20shed.%20Pavan%2C%20then%2C%20went%20to%20a%20club%20where%20Darshan%20was%20partying%20with%20friends%20and%20showed%20him%20the%20photos.%20After%20seeing%20the%20photos%2C%20Darshan%20went%20to%20actor%20Pavithra%20Gowda's%20home%20and%20brought%20her%20to%20the%20shed%20where%20they%20continued%20the%20assault%20on%20Renukaswamy%2C%20IANS%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20chargesheet%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20Police%20detailed%20the%20alleged%20brutal%20torture%20before%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20being%20assaulted%20by%20Darshan%20and%20his%20gang%2C%20Renukaswamy's%20chest%20bones%20were%20broken.%20There%20are%20a%20total%20of%2039%20injury%20marks%20all%20over%20his%20body.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20deep%20cut%20on%20the%20victim's%20head%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20chargesheet%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20said%20that%20Darshan%20and%20his%20aides%20used%20an%20electrical%20device%20to%20deliver%20electric%20shocks%20to%20Renukaswamy's%20private%20parts%20to%20jolt%20him%20awake%20when%20he%20passed%20out%20from%20pain%20after%20being%20repeatedly%20assaulted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20committing%20the%20murder%2C%20Darshan%20and%20the%20other%20accused%20used%20their%20influence%20and%20money%20to%20dispose%20of%20the%20body%20and%20attempted%20to%20destroy%20evidence.%20They%20also%20tried%20to%20frame%20other%20individuals%20to%20escape%20charges%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20chargesheet%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kannada%20actor%20is%20among%2017%20people%2C%20including%20his%20friend%20actor%20Pavithra%20Gowda%2C%20who%20are%20in%20judicial%20custody%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20murder%20of%20his%20fan%20Renukaswamy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2033-year-old%20fan%20had%20allegedly%20sent%20obscene%20messages%20to%20Pavithra%20Gowda%2C%20after%20which%20he%20was%20allegedly%20beaten%20to%20death.%20His%20body%20was%20found%20near%20a%20stormwater%20drain%20in%20Bengaluru's%20Sumanahalli%20on%20June%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725518640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fraq647_actor-darshan_625x300_04_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-murder-case-against-actor-darshan-photos-of-assault-on-victim-surface-6495168%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20new%20twist%20in%20the%20kidnap%20and%20murder%20case%20against%20Kannada%20actor%20Darshan%2C%20photos%20allegedly%20showing%20the%20victim%20Renukaswamy%20being%20tortured%20before%20his%20death%20have%20surfaced%20on%20Th