2Indian-Origin%20Star%2C%20Who%20Played%2053%20T20Is%20For%20Ireland%2C%20Battling%20For%20Life%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian-origin%20all-rounder%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Simi%20Singh%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107658-simi-singh-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESimi%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20has%20played%2035%20ODIs%20and%2053%20T20Is%20for%20Ireland%2C%20is%20currently%20battling%20for%20his%20life.%20The%20cricketer%2C%20who%20is%20suffering%20from%20acute%20liver%20failure%2C%20is%20currently%20in%20the%20ICU%20of%20a%20Gurugram%20hospital%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fexclusive-cricketer-simranjit-singh-battling-for-life%2Farticleshow%2F113078583.cms%5C%22%3ETimes%20Of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20report%20further%20stated%20that%20the%20cricketer%20is%20waiting%20for%20a%20liver%20transplant%20that%20will%20be%20performed%20at%20the%20hospital.%20Simi%2C%20who%20was%20born%20in%20Mohali%2C%20played%20for%20Punjab%20at%20the%20U-14%20and%20U-17%20levels%20but%20failed%20to%20make%20the%20U-19%20team.%20He%20decided%20to%20travel%20to%20Ireland%20for%20studying%20hotel%20management%20and%20in%202006%2C%20he%20joined%C2%A0Malahide%20Cricket%20Club%20in%20Dublin%20as%20a%20professional.%20He%20went%20on%20to%20become%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20cricketers%20for%20Ireland%20with%2039%20ODI%20wickets%20and%2044%20T20I%20wickets.%20He%20has%20also%20scored%20an%20ODI%20century%20against%20South%20Africa%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimi%20Singh's%20father-in-law%C2%A0Parvinder%20Singh%20opened%20up%20about%20the%20cricketer's%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20five-six%20months%20back%2C%20when%20he%20was%20in%20Dublin%2C%20Ireland%2C%20Simi%20developed%20a%20strange%20kind%20of%20fever%20which%20kept%20coming%20and%20going.%20He%20got%20himself%20examined%20there%2C%20but%20nothing%20conclusive%20came%20out%20in%20the%20check-ups.%20The%20medical%20professionals%20there%20said%20that%20they%20couldn't%20find%20the%20underlying%20cause%20and%20therefore%20they%20wouldn't%20start%20medication%2C%26quot%3B%20Parvinder%20told%20Times%20Of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20process%20was%20getting%20delayed%20and%20Simi's%20health%20was%20deteriorating%2C%20so%20we%20decided%20to%20get%20him%20treated%20in%20India%20for%20'better%20medical%20attention'.%20Simi%20flew%20to%20Mohali%20in%20late%20June%2C%20and%20after%20a%20few%20consultations%20with%20various%20physicians%20his%20treatment%20started%20in%20PGI%2C%20Chandigarh%20in%20the%20beginning%20of%20July.%20There%20the%20line%20of%20treatment%20was%20taken%20for%20TB%20(tuberculosis)%20and%20antibiotics%20were%20given%20to%20him.%20Later%2C%20results%20came%20out%20that%20he%20didn't%20have%20TB.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20his%20fever%20didn't%20subside%2C%20we%20took%20him%20to%20a%20private%20hospital%20in%20Mohali%20for%20a%20second%20opinion.%20There%2C%20we%20were%20told%20that%20Simi%20didn't%20have%20TB%2C%20but%20the%20course%20of%20the%20medicines%20-%20six%20weeks%20-%20had%20to%20be%20completed.%20Along%20with%20the%20TB%20medicines%2C%20steroids%20were%20also%20given%20to%20him.%20After%20that%2C%20his%20fever%20started%20increasing%20again%20and%20he%20developed%20acute%20jaundice.%20In%20the%20last%20week%20of%20August%2C%20we%20took%20him%20back%20to%20PGI%20where%20he%20was%20admitted%20to%20the%20ICU.%20But%20his%20health%20kept%20deteriorating%20and%20the%20PGI%20physicians%20detected%20that%20he%20had%20developed%20acute%20liver%20failure.%20They%20advised%20us%20to%20take%20Simi%20to%20Medanta%2C%20Gurugram%2C%20because%20there%20was%20a%20high%20probability%20of%20him%20slipping%20into%20coma%20after%20which%20a%20transplant%20wouldn't%20be%20possible.%20We%20came%20to%20Medanta%20on%20September%203%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20Simi%20is%20now%20waiting%20for%20a%20liver%20transplant%20and%20his%20wife%20-%20Agamdeep%20Kaur%20-%20has%20agreed%20to%20donate%20one%20part%20of%20her%20liver.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725516840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-01%2Firmcnj2_simi-singh-afp_625x300_08_January_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Findian-origin-star-who-played-53-t20is-for-ireland-battling-for-life-6494882%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian-origin%20all-rounder%20Simi%20Singh%2C%20who%20has%20played%2035%20ODIs%20and%2053%20T20Is%20for%20Ireland%2C%20is%20currently%20battling%20for%20his%20life.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Findian-origin-star-who-played-53-t20is-for-ireland-battling-for-life-6494882%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe%20Perform%20Last%20Rites%20Of%20Evil%20Forces%20When%20They%20Reach%20India%26quot%3B%3A%20RSS%20Chief%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20Chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20has%20stated%20that%20while%20evil%20forces%20grow%20larger%20across%20the%20globe%2C%20they%20eventually%20face%20decline%20when%20they%20reach%20India%2C%20where%20%26quot%3Bwe%20perform%20their%20last%20rites.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20made%20these%20remarks%20on%20Wednesday%20during%20the%20'Vedsevak%20Sanman%20Sohala%2C'%20an%20award%20ceremony%20organised%20by%20the%20Sadguru%20Group%20to%20felicitate%20200%20'gurujis'%20who%20participated%20in%20the%20'anushthan'%20(rituals)%20of%20the%20four%20Vedas%20for%2016%20months%20during%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20in%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhagwat%20noted%20that%20evil%20forces%20are%20always%20active%20and%20united%2C%20requiring%20no%20coaching%2C%20unlike%20virtuous%20people%2C%20who%20need%20to%20meet%20frequently%20to%20receive%20guidance%20and%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvil%20Forces%20exist%20globally%2C%20with%20their%20evil%20acts%20occurring%20everywhere.%20Bangladesh%20is%20not%20the%20first%20case.%20The%20first%20case%20is%20America.%20I%20read%20a%20book%20by%20an%20American%20author%20titled%20Cultural%20Development%20of%20America%2C%20which%20discusses%20the%20cultural%20degradation%20in%20America%20over%20the%20last%20100%20years.%20This%20degradation%20was%20replicated%20in%20Poland%2C%20then%20spread%20to%20Arab%20countries%20during%20the%20Arab%20Spring%2C%20and%20recently%20it%20happened%20in%20Bangladesh.%20Those%20who%20seek%20to%20tighten%20their%20grip%20on%20the%20world%20and%20believe%20they%20are%20the%20only%20ones%20who%20are%20right--while%20others%20are%20wrong--are%20the%20ones%20who%20promote%20these%20divisive%20tendencies%20for%20their%20own%20benefit%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhagwat%20emphasised%20that%20such%20tendencies%20lead%20to%20catastrophes%20and%20the%20downfall%20of%20nations.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20monitor%20these%20tendencies%20without%20fear.%20History%20shows%20that%20while%20these%20tendencies%20grow%20larger%20and%20eventually%20reach%20India%2C%20they%20decline%20here%20as%20we%20perform%20their%20last%20rites.%20This%20is%20possible%20because%20we%20possess%20the%20knowledge%20to%20tame%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RSS%20chief%20also%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20increasing%20disbelief%20(anastha%20and%20ashraddha)%2C%20particularly%20among%20the%20educated%20class%2C%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20role%20models.%20%26quot%3BIdeals%20exist%2C%20but%20if%20a%20person%20is%20to%20change%2C%20there%20must%20be%20someone%20around%20to%20guide%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20remarked%20that%20untouchability%20has%20no%20basis%20in%20the%20Shastras%20(Hindu%20scriptures)%2C%20yet%20it%20persists.%20%26quot%3BIf%20someone%2C%20frustrated%20with%20the%20stubborn%20practices%20within%20Hinduism%2C%20converts%20to%20another%20religion%2C%20who%20is%20to%20blame%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725516780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fjfuuv0v8_rss-chief-mohan-bhagwat_625x300_15_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frss-chief-mohan-bhagwat-says-we-perform-last-rites-of-evil-forces-when-they-reach-india-6493232%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20Chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20has%20stated%20that%20while%20evil%20forces%20grow%20larger%20across%20the%20globe%2C%20they%20eventually%20face%20decline%20when%20they%20reach%20India%2C%20where%20%26quot%3Bwe%20perform%20their%20last%20rites.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frss-chief-mohan-bhagwat-says-we-perform-last-rites-of-evil-forces-when-they-reach-india-6493232%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Excise%20policy%20scam%3A%20SC%20begins%20hearing%20Kejriwal's%20plea%20against%20CBI%20arrest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725516626000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-07%2F01%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1719809615-6194.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fexcise-policy-scam-sc-begins-hearing-kejriwal-s-plea-against-cbi-arrest-124090500358_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kejriwal%20has%20filed%20two%20separate%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20denial%20of%20bail%20and%20against%20his%20arrest%20by%20the%20CBI%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%