e%20second%20quarter%2C%20beating%20many%20analysts'%20estimates%20for%20the%20period.%20Nearly%20half%20of%20that%20came%20from%20four%20customers%2C%20according%20to%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fd18rn0p25nwr6d.cloudfront.net%2FCIK-0001045810%2F78501ce3-7816-4c4d-8688-53dd140df456.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESEC%20filing%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20should%20keep%20investors%20on%20alert%20for%20the%20next%20year%20or%20two%2C%20Gil%20Luria%2C%20a%20tech%20analyst%20who%20covers%20Nvidia%20for%20D.A.%20Davidson%2C%20an%20investment%20firm%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20company%20filing%2C%20just%20four%20customers%20brought%20in%2046%25%20of%20Nvidia's%20total%20Q2%20revenue%20%E2%80%94%20about%20%2413.8%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20companies%20are%20kept%20anonymous%20in%20the%20filing.%20There's%20no%20disclosure%20law%20that%20requires%20Nvidia%20to%20reveal%20its%20clients'%20names%2C%20Luria%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20customers%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-gpu-targets-1-8-million-ai-chips-this-year-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-mark-zuckerberg-ai-chips-gpus-meta-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-nvidia-aws-ai-chip-dominance-gpu-trainium-inferentia-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdeveloper.nvidia.com%2Fblog%2Fgoogle-cloud-run-adds-support-for-nvidia-l4-gpus-nvidia-nim-and-serverless-ai-inference-deployments-at-scale%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DGoogle%2520Cloud%2520was%2520the%2520first%2CGKE)%252C%2520and%2520Vertex%2520AI.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Luria%20said.%20All%20four%20companies%20are%20known%20to%20be%20ramping%20up%20their%20GPU%20stockpiles%20as%20they%20aggressively%20pursue%20AI%20initiatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20only%20way%20that%20they're%20not%20the%20four%20is%20if%20one%20of%20their%20customers%20is%20a%20reseller%2C%26quot%3B%20Luria%20said%2C%20naming%20Dell%20and%20Supermicro%20as%20examples.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Nvidia%20spokesperson%20declined%20to%20comment%2C%20and%20none%20of%20the%20four%20purported%20customers%20responded%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuria%20said%20it's%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20unusual%20for%20a%20company%26quot%3B%20at%20Nvidia's%20scale%20to%20lean%20on%20a%20handful%20of%20clients%20for%20a%20large%20chunk%20of%20its%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNone%20of%20the%20other%20mega%20caps%20even%20have%20one%2010%25%20customer%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20tech%20analyst%20told%20BI%2C%20referring%20to%20large%20companies%20with%20a%20market%20capitalization%20of%20more%20than%20%24200%20billion.%20As%20of%20Wednesday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-ai-3-trillion-club-apple-microsoft-jensen-huang-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia's%20market%20cap%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20%242.61%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuria%20maintained%20a%20Hold%20rating%20for%20Nvidia%20stock%2C%20citing%20concerns%20around%20the%20sustainability%20of%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJacob%20Bourne%2C%20a%20tech%20analyst%20for%20Emarketer%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20high%20concentration%20of%20revenue%20may%20be%20unusual%20within%20the%20context%20of%20the%20broader%20marketplace.%20But%20he%20said%20it's%20normal%20for%20tech%20companies%20that%20provide%20a%20specialized%20product%2C%20like%20graphics%20processing%20units.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmarketer%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20Axel%20Springer%2C%20which%20also%20owns%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20said%20in%20a%2010-Q%20filing%20that%20it%20has%20experienced%20periods%20where%20the%20company%20saw%20a%20significant%20amount%20of%20revenue%20from%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20customers%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bthis%20trend%20may%20continue.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202004%20%E2%80%94%20when%20Nvidia%20was%20bringing%20in%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20revenue%20it's%20seeing%20today%20%E2%80%94%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fd18rn0p25nwr6d.cloudfront.net%2FCIK-0001045810%2Fac23c11f-a5bf-40d7-be57-051de2280872.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompany's%2010-Q%20filing%3C%2Fa%3E%20showed%20that%20just%20four%20unnamed%20customers%20brought%20in%2051%25%20of%20its%20total%20revenue%20in%20the%20third%20quarter.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Nvidia%20was%20working%20with%20PC%20manufacturers%20like%20Dell%20and%20Sony%20to%20provide%20GPUs%20for%20computer%20and%20gaming%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuria%20told%20BI%20that%20Nvidia%20has%20historically%20maintained%20the%20same%20big%20four%20customers%20%E2%80%94%20Microsoft%2C%20Meta%2C%20Amazon%2C%20and%20Google%20%E2%80%94%20in%20its%20data%20center%20segment.%20But%20they%20have%20typically%20been%20balanced%20by%20Nvidia's%20gaming%20and%20auto%20segments%2C%20which%20have%20different%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCustomer%20concentration%20has%20increased%20for%20NVDIA%20recently%20because%20the%20data%20center%20business%20is%20now%20a%20much%20bigger%20proportion%20of%20overall%20revenue%2C%26quot%3B%20Luria%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20this%20customer%20concentration%20should%20be%20investors'%20primary%20concern%20for%20the%20next%20year%20or%20two%20for%20three%20key%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ereasons%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2219794bc8-2282-4325-ab93-849ca43c06d0%5C%22%3E1.%20Large%20companies%20don't%20rely%20on%20a%20single%20source%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBig%20companies%20%26quot%3Bdon't%20like%20being%20beholden%20to%20one%20vendor%20for%20any%20category%2C%26quot%3B%20Luria%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20like%20Walmart%20doesn't%20buy%20all%20of%20its%20potato%20chips%20from%20one%20vendor%2C%20Microsoft%20doesn't%20like%20buying%20its%20computer%20chips%20from%20one%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20has%20made%20that%20clear%20before%2C%20Luria%20added%2C%20citing%20how%20the%20company%20gradually%20moved%20away%20from%20Intel%20as%20its%20sole%20provider%20for%20processors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e614e1af-bc45-45a4-b47a-21a151d95099%5C%22%3E2.%20The%20Nvidia%20demand%20could%20be%20temporary%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20reason%20investors%20should%20be%20concerned%20is%20that%20these%20large%20Nvidia%20customers%20have%20indicated%20that%20they%20are%20buying%20more%20GPUs%20without%20concern%20for%20their%20immediate%20return%20on%20investment%2C%20Luria%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20companies%20%26quot%3Bhave%20communicated%20that%20they%20are%20'over-investing%2C'%20which%20means%20they%20are%20buying%20without%20regard%20for%20a%20return%20on%20investment%2C%20usually%20not%20something%20that%20lasts%20very%20long%2C%26quot%3B%20Luria%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-q1-results-ai-investment-payoff-mark-zuckerberg-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20shareholders%20during%20an%20earnings%20call%20in%20April%20that%20any%20upside%20to%20his%20company's%20AI%20pursuits%20will%20likely%20%26quot%3Btake%20several%20years%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20so%20the%20current%20feeding%20frenzy%20for%20Nvidia%20chips%20from%20the%20large%20clients%20could%20be%20temporary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20doesn't%20mean%20Nvidia%20will%20lack%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBourne%2C%20the%20Emarketer%20analyst%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20Nvidia%20has%20a%20long%20list%20of%20clients%2C%20from%20countries%20to%20startups%2C%20that%20want%20to%20buy%20the%20company's%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20because%20currently%20there's%20these%20handful%20of%20companies%20that%20are%20r