ctor's%20Parents%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERaising%20big%20questions%20about%20the%20Kolkata%20Police's%20response%20after%20the%20horrifying%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20doctor%20at%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%2C%20the%20victim's%20parents%20have%20alleged%20that%20they%20wanted%20the%20body%20preserved%2C%20but%20were%20forced%20to%20proceed%20with%20the%20cremation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParents%20and%20relatives%20of%20the%2031-year-old%20doctor%20attended%20the%20protests%20outside%20the%20state-run%20hospital%20last%20night.%20Levelling%20serious%20charges%20against%20the%20city%20cops%2C%20the%20victim's%20father%20said%20a%20senior%20police%20officer%20offered%20them%20money%20when%20their%20daughter's%20body%20was%20in%20front%20of%20them%2C%20according%20to%20reports%20in%20local%20media.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20wanted%20the%20body%20preserved%2C%20but%20so%20much%20pressure%20was%20created.%20About%20300-400%20cops%20surrounded%20us.%20We%20returned%20home%20and%20found%20some%20300%20cops%20were%20standing%20outside.%20They%20created%20such%20a%20situation%20that%20we%20were%20forced%20to%20cremate%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%20He%20also%20said%20the%20cremation%20was%20rushed%20and%20the%20cost%20was%20not%20taken%20from%20the%20family.%20%26quot%3BMy%20daughter%20went%20knowing%20that%20Bapi%20(father)%20could%20not%20even%20pay%20for%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20victim's%20father%20said.%20He%20also%20alleged%20that%20some%20police%20officers%20tried%20to%20get%20his%20signature%20on%20a%20blank%20sheet%20of%20paper.%20%26quot%3BI%20tore%20it%20up%20and%20threw%20it%20away.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20my%20daughter's%20body%20was%20at%20our%20home%2C%20DC%20North%20tried%20to%20give%20us%20some%20money.%20We%20replied%20to%20him%20accordingly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20full%20support%20to%20the%20doctors%20protesting%20at%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20in%20demand%20of%20justice%20for%20their%20friend%20and%20colleague%2C%20the%20victim's%20mother%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20sleep.%20I%20want%20the%20criminals%20to%20lose%20sleep%20too.%20The%20protest%20should%20continue%20till%20we%20get%20justice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim's%20father%20questioned%20why%20hospital%20authorities%20told%20them%20even%20before%20the%20body%20was%20examined%20that%20their%20daughter%20had%20died%20by%20suicide.%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20to%20wait%20for%20three-and-a-half%20hours%20to%20see%20our%20daughter's%20face.%20Her%20mother%20fell%20on%20their%20feet%20to%20let%20us%20see%20her.%20Why%20was%20autopsy%20delayed%3F%20Why%20did%20police%20file%20an%20unnatural%20death%20case%3F%20I%20filed%20the%20complaint%20at%20Tala%20Police%20Station%20around%207%20pm.%20Why%20then%20was%20FIR%20registered%20at%2011.45%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sequence%20of%20events%20after%20the%20doctor's%20body%20was%20found%20in%20the%20hospital's%20seminar%20hall%20has%20repeatedly%20come%20under%20the%20scanner%20in%20the%20courts.%20While%20Kolkata%20Police%20has%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20its%20affidavit%20that%20the%20victim's%20parents%20had%20to%20wait%20for%20just%2010%20minutes%20before%20they%20were%20taken%20to%20the%20seminar%20hall%20where%20the%20body%20was%20found%2C%20the%20parents%20have%20stressed%20that%20they%20waited%20for%20over%20three%20hours%20and%20begged%20the%20cops%20to%20let%20them%20see%20their%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20have%20also%20questioned%20why%20the%20hospital%20administration%20did%20not%20file%20a%20police%20complaint%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20cops%20registering%20an%20unnatural%20death%20case.%20The%20delay%20in%20filing%20the%20FIR%20has%20also%20raised%20questions.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20the%20reason%20the%20FIR%20is%20lodged%20almost%2014%20hours%20after%20the%20discovery%20of%20the%20(body)%3F%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20asked%20during%20the%20hearing%20in%20Supreme%20Court.%20Senior%20Advocate%20Kapil%20Sibal%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government%2C%20has%20stressed%20the%20cops%20followed%20procedure%20to%20a%20tee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim's%20parents%20had%20earlier%20approached%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%2C%20following%20which%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20case%20was%20transferred%20to%20CBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKolkata%20continues%20to%20witnessed%20massive%20protests%20against%20the%20August%209%20incident.%20Last%20night%2C%20residents%20of%20the%20city%20turned%20off%20their%20lights%20for%20an%20hour%20to%20demand%20justice%20for%20the%20victim.%20Lights%20were%20also%20turned%20off%20at%20the%20landmarks%20such%20as%20Victoria%20Memorial%20and%20Raj%20Bhavan%20as%20part%20of%20the%20protest.%20Governor%20CV%20Ananda%20Bose%20lit%20candles%20at%20Raj%20Bhavan%20and%20shared%20visuals%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20light%20is%20fear%2C%20darkness%20is%20dear%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20the%20caption.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725511680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F3a9ne31_kolkata-protest_625x300_05_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-doctor-rape-murder-rg-kar-medical-college-wanted-body-preserved-forced-to-cremate-kolkata-doctors-parents-6494375%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Raising%20big%20questions%20about%20the%20Kolkata%20Police's%20response%20after%20the%20horrifying%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20doctor%20at%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%2C%20victim's%20parents%20have%20alleged%20they%20wanted%20the%20body%20preserved%2C%20but%20were%20forced%20to%20proceed%20with%20cremation%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-doctor-rape-murder-rg-kar-medica