mixed%20compound%20open%20category%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarvinder%2C%20the%20first%20Indian%20Paralympic%20medallist%20in%20archery%2C%20dispatched%20world%20No.%209%20Hector%20Julio%20Ramirez%20of%20Colombia%206-2%20in%20the%20quarterfinals%2C%20having%20earlier%20eliminated%20Tseng%20Lung-Hui%20of%20Chinese%20Taipei%207-3%20in%20the%20round%20of%2032.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20pre-quarters%2C%20he%20rallied%20from%20an%20initial%20set%20deficit%20to%20edge%20out%20Setiawan%20Setiawan%20of%20Indonesia%206-2.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20became%20the%20first%20Indian%20archer%20to%20enter%20the%20Paralympic%20final%20when%20he%20overturned%20a%201-3%20deficit%20to%20triumph%20over%20Iran's%20Mohammad%20Reza%20Arab%20Ameri%207-3.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20each%20of%20his%20victories%2C%20Harvinder%20showcased%20his%20resilience%2C%20consistently%20staging%20comebacks%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20hunt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20final%2C%20Harvinder%20Singh%20displayed%20a%20different%20level%20of%20precision%2C%20conceding%20only%20two%20points%20to%20secure%20the%20first%20set%20with%20a%20commanding%20four-point%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Ciszek%20rallied%20in%20the%20second%20set%2C%20landing%20three%209s%2C%20Harvinder's%20unflinching%20focus%20and%20consistent%20shooting%20--%20scoring%20another%2028%20--%20enabled%20him%20to%20edge%20out%20Ciszek%20by%20a%20single%20point%2C%20extending%20his%20lead%20to%204-0.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarvinder%20Singh%20delivered%20a%20hat-trick%20of%2010s%2C%20including%20a%20perfect%20inner%2010%20(X)%2C%20intensifying%20the%20pressure%20on%20his%20opponent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiszek%20faltered%20with%20a%207%20and%20followed%20with%20a%209%2C%20while%20Harvinder%20clinched%20the%20gold%20with%20a%20decisive%209%20on%20his%20final%20arrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20stands%2C%20Sheetal%20Devi%20was%20seen%20celebrating%20exuberantly%20as%20Harvinder%20bowed%2C%20embraced%20his%20coach%2C%20and%20proudly%20waved%20the%20Tricolour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20semifinal%2C%20Harvinder%20narrowly%20dropped%20the%20first%20set%2025-26%20and%20tied%20the%20second%2027-27.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaintaining%20his%20composure%2C%20Harvinder%20delivered%20splendid%20performances%20with%20successive%2010s%20on%20his%20final%20arrows%20of%20the%20third%20and%20fourth%20sets%2C%20clinching%20them%2027-25%20and%2026-24%20to%20take%20a%205-3%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeeding%20a%20set%20win%20in%20the%20final%20end%20to%20avoid%20a%20shoot-off%2C%20Harvinder%20faced%20a%20strong%20challenge%20from%20Ameri%2C%20who%20opened%20with%20an%20X%20(inner%2010)%20and%20followed%20with%20an%208%20to%20level%20the%20set%20at%2018-18%2C%20setting%20up%20a%20tense%20final%20arrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20pressure%2C%20Ameri%20faltered%20with%20a%207%2C%20allowing%20Harvinder%20to%20close%20out%20the%20match%20with%20an%208%20and%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recurve%20open%20class%2C%20archers%20shoot%20from%20a%20standing%20position%20at%20a%20distance%20of%2070m%20at%20a%20122cm%20target%20made%20up%20of%2010%20concentric%20circles%2C%20scoring%20from%2010%20points%20down%20to%201%20point%20from%20the%20centre%20outwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20a%20family%20of%20farmers%20from%20Ajit%20Nagar%20in%20Haryana%2C%20Harvinder%20faced%20significant%20adversity%20early%20in%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20was%20just%20one%20and%20a%20half%20years%20old%2C%20he%20contracted%20dengue%20and%20due%20to%20the%20side%20effects%20of%20some%20injections%20administered%20to%20him%2C%20both%20his%20legs%20were%20left%20impaired.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%20early%20challenge%2C%20he%20found%20a%20passion%20for%20archery%20after%20getting%20inspiration%20from%202012%20London%20Paralympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20made%20his%20debut%20at%20the%202017%20Para%20Archery%20World%20Championship%2C%20finishing%20seventh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20gold%20medal%20at%20th