0Meenakshi%20Chaudhary%20play%20the%20lead%20female%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20strong%20advance%20bookings%2C%20GOAT%20is%20expected%20to%20perform%20exceptionally%20well%20at%20the%20box%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%2C%20Director%20Venkat%20Prabhu%20discussed%20the%20making%20of%20the%20film%20and%20the%20joys%20of%20working%20with%20Vijay.%20He%20revealed%20that%20he%20used%20de-aging%20technology%20to%20differentiate%20between%20Vijay's%20two%20characters%2C%20a%20first%20for%20Indian%20cinema.%20Mr%20Prabhu%20also%20praised%20Vijay's%20professionalism%20and%20dedication%20to%20his%20craft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay%2C%20known%20for%20his%20quiet%20demeanor%20on%20sets%2C%20has%20been%20preparing%20for%20his%20political%20career.%20While%20he%20has%20avoided%20making%20any%20political%20statements%2C%20Mr%20Prabhu%20hinted%20that%20Vijay's%20approach%20to%20politics%20might%20be%20similar%20to%20his%20on-screen%20persona.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGOAT%20features%20a%20strong%20ensemble%20cast%20including%20Prabhu%20Deva%2C%20Jayaram%2C%20Mohan%20and%20%C2%A0Prashanth%20with%20both%20Sneha%20and%20Meenakshi%20Chaudhary%20playing%20female%20leads.%20The%20film%20also%20marks%20the%20reunion%20of%20Vijay%20and%20Sneha%20after%2020%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20of%20GOAT%20comes%20amid%20the%20recent%20HEMA%20Committee%20report%20in%20Kerala%20that%20has%20sparked%20important%20conversations%20about%20the%20need%20for%20a%20safer%20working%20environment%20for%20women%20in%20the%20industry.%20The%20director%20also%20emphasized%20the%20need%20for%20the%20Tamil%20film%20industry%20to%20address%20sexual%20harassment%20allegations%2C%20ensuring%20punishment%20for%20perpetrators%20to%20create%20a%20safer%20environment%20for%20women.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20against%20Lyricist%20Vairamuthu%20and%20Actor%20Radha%20Ravi%20by%20Singer%20Chinmayi%2C%20Venkat%20Prabhu