ue%20was%20close%20to%20her%20heart.%20We%20thought%20that%20this%20could%20be%20a%20good%20idea%20as%20it%20was%20difficult%20for%20us%20also%20to%20tap%20into%20the%20talents%20of%20artisans%20who%20live%20in%20far%20off%20tribal%20villages.%20We%20decided%20to%20marry%20both%20the%20concepts%20of%20upcycling%20fabric%20waste%20and%20generating%20employment%20for%20refugee%20women%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20do%20something%20meaningful%2C%20Bishwadeep%20quit%20his%20job%20as%20an%20executive%20editor%20at%20Outlook%20news%20magazine%20and%20co-founded%20SilaiWali%20along%20with%20his%20wife.%20%E2%80%9CJournalism%20allowed%20me%20a%20way%20to%20work%20for%20society%20but%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20differently%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20of%20service%20to%20society%20in%20a%20direct%20way.%20I%20was%20motivated%20by%20my%20wife%20to%20work%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThereafter%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20start%20SilaiWali%20in%202018%20for%20financial%20independence%20of%20Afghan%20women%20refugees%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSilaiWali-2-1725019714.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Currently%2C%20Iris%20and%20Bishwadeep%20are%20providing%20a%20livelihood%20to%20more%20than%2070%20Afghan%20refugee%20women.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSilaiWali-2-1725019714.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSilaiWali-2-1725019714-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSilaiWali-2-1725019714-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSilaiWali-2-